        "text": "パイモンの絵シリーズ vol.21"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/27/317536791/4bce61eb4672ca32edfee57841bcf0bb_7944243364195233450.png",
